      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Trace Bridge\n\n- **Trace ID**: `${traceId}`\n- **Execution ID**: `${executionId}`\n- **Target Agent**: `${targetAgent}`\n- **Focus Service**: `${focusService}`\n- **Node ID**: `${nodeId}`\n\n控制台会把 execution / node 焦点通过 dashboard variables 深链进来。你可以先看下面的 drill-down 指标，再切到右侧 Service Graph Map 理解链路位置。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Trace Bridge Context",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "DishAgentPrometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" } }, "overrides": [] },
